# Repository safety
# This repository lives inside the installed game directory.
# Ignore everything first, then allow only the Korean localization project files.

/*
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/README.md
!/HXSS_Korean_Localization/
!/HXSS_Korean_Localization/**

# Generated release binaries should be uploaded to GitHub Releases, not committed.
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/ReleasePackages/**
!/HXSS_Korean_Localization/ReleasePackages/
!/HXSS_Korean_Localization/ReleasePackages/README.md

# Local archives and bundled runtime snapshots
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/99_Cleanup_Archive/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/BepInEx-Unity.IL2CPP-win-x64-6.0.0-be.755+3fab71a/**

# Historical/generated localization outputs
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/Release/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/SourceSnapshot/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/WorkingXml/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/Review/Archive_Raw/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/Review/Archive_Legacy_Audits_*/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/XmlWork/Review/Archive_Working_Audits_*/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/01_XML_Localization/번역 이슈 스크린샷/**

# Generated caches and working outputs
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/bin/
**/obj/
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/MaintenanceKit/cache/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/MaintenanceKit/output/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/MaintenanceKit/luac.out

# Local tool runtimes and extracted font/source material
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/03_Font_Work/Font/.dotnet_home/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/03_Font_Work/Font/dotnet_home/**
/HXSS_Korean_Localization/03_Font_Work/Font/추출 폰트/**

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.exe
*.dll
*.pdb
